title.rendered: BOSS AIR DIGITAL LED GAUGE PANEL & SWITCHES

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR DIGITAL LED GAUGE PANEL & SWITCHES

Boss Air Digital Dual LED Gauge Panel & Switches available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Features:

  • 0-220psi
  • Blue LED Dual Display
  • Twin sensors with 1/8″ NPT thread
  • Auto Light Dim Function
  • LED Momentary Switches
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
